{"id":658161,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/10/人是最美的风景-泰国人民欢度传统泼水佳节/","date":"2020-10-20T16:30:58Z","modified":"2020-10-21T01:22:22Z","title":"人是最美的风景 | 泰国人民欢度传统泼水佳节","content":"<div>CDT编者按：本篇文章以“泼水节”为名发表泰国示威运动图片，在微信平台上广为流传。</div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>泰国的泼水节，又叫宋干节，就像中国的春节，是泰国新年的开始。这时候大家团聚在一起，互相泼水祝福，消除邪恶和不幸，开始美好的一年。随着泼水节影响的逐渐扩大，活动越来越丰富，现在越来越多的警察也加入到泼水节的行列，警民一家亲，其乐共融融。<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span></p>\n<p>——洋葱百科</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-658162\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威1.jpg 1074w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威1-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-658163\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威2.jpg 780w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威2-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-658164\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威3.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威3-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/10/泰国示威3-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 5